    {
        "url": "/quotes/harvey_pekar_604224",
        "quote": "I was 16 years old, and I was just flailing around, looking for an interest. I heard, you know, these jazz records. They were modern records, at the time in the '50s, and I realized that I didn't fully get what was going on. But I liked a lot of what I heard.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Harvey Pekar",
            "url": "/quotes/harvey_pekar_604224"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Jazz",
                "url": "/topics/jazz"
