    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/harvey_pekar_604249",
        "quote": "I guess I wanted to show people, among other things, that you don't have to be a hero to get through cancer. You can be a craven coward and get through. You have to stay on your medication and take your treatments, that's all.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Harvey Pekar",
            "url": "/quotes/harvey_pekar_604249"
